high_descs: Turn around, head towards the toaster, and then turn right towards metal pan on the counter.
Pick up the metal pan from the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Place the pan in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn right and head towards the toaster on the counter.
Place the pan to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed pan to the left of the toaster.

high_descs: Turn around to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick the square pan up from the counter.
Move left to stand in front of the sink.
Put the pan in the sink, turn the water on and then turn it off and take the pan out of the sink.
Turn around and stand to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Put the pan down on the counter to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, then go straight, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the pan from on the counter, to the right of the bowl.
Go to the sink to your left.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn around, move forward, then turn left to approach the counter located to the right of the stove.
Put the pan on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and approach the stove.
Pick up the pan on the counter to the left of the stove.
Move to the left to stand at the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn right and go back to the stove.
Put the pan on the counter between the stove and the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to where the toaster is on the counter, then turn left and walk over to the section of counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the dirty pan that is on the counter to the right of the butter knife.
Turn left and take a couple steps forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the dirty pan in the sink basin and turn on the water to clean it, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean pan.
Turn around and take a couple steps, then turn left and walk up to the toaster on the counter.
Place the clean pan on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on the counter.
